quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Indukho ili hambi okhwitsa, ne omwesi kwabukhamwo (tsinyanga tsia Omurumwa Muhammad)."
  54,2,"Ne nibalola eshimanyisio shiosishiosi bashifutarira nibaboola mbu: “Buno nobulosi butsilililanga.”"
  54,3,"Ne baingasia, ne nibaloonda eshihonya shiabu, ne buli likhuwa liemekhwa."
  54,4,"Ne toto kamala okhuboolela amakhuwa kalimwo okhwalaba."
  54,5,"Amachesi kafung’anile, halali amekanyilisio shikakhoonya eshindu khubo tawe."
  54,6,"Mana lekhana ninabo (nibalobere okhulunjikha). Inyanga yalilaanga omulaanji khushindu shilamanyishe tawe."
  54,7,"Tsimoni tsiabwe tsilihenga hasi. Balirula mubilindwa opara mbu nitsisiche tsisaalanibwe."
  54,8,"Nibelushila Omulaanji oyo, ne Abakhayi baliboola mbu: “Inyanga ino ni indinyu.”"
  54,9,"Abandu ba Nuhu bakhaya bo nibashili, nibayingasia Omusumba wefu, nibamuboolela mbu nomulalu mana nibamwalabila."
  54,10,"Mana nasaba Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, naboola mbu: “Toto esie ekhailwe, kho habina.”"
  54,11,"Mana nikhwikula emiliango chomwikulu khu maatsi kayombokhanga."
  54,12,"Ne nikhufutula liloba nikhukhola emialo (emichela), amaatsi nikabukanana (kamwikulu nende kamwiloba) khulikhuwa liali nilibusibwe (okhusishibwa abandu ba Nuhu mumaatsi)."
  54,13,"Ne nikhubachinga khushietsimbao nende emisumari (Isafina)."
  54,14,"Shiatsitsanga khubwemeresi bwefu, okhuba ni omurungo khu balia abakhaya ka Nyasaye."
  54,15,"Ne toto bwene khwachikhola okhuba eshimanyisio. Ne koo, aliwo witsulila?"
  54,16,"Kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie, nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje?"
  54,17,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu khubwitsulisio, ne koo aliwo witsulila?"
  54,18,"Babu A’di bakhaya, kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje?"
  54,19,"Toto efwe khwabarumila omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka khutsinyanga tsimbi tsilondokhaane."
  54,20,"Nikusiula Abandu opara mbu nebisichiri biemisala chisiulilwe."
  54,21,"Mana eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende amekanyilisio kanje?"
  54,22,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu khubwitsulisio. Ne koo, aliwo witsulila?"
  54,23,"Abandu ba Thamudi bayingasia Abekanyilisi."
  54,24,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khuloonde omundu namundu urula mwifwe. Efwe mana khuba khulaba mubukori bwa habulafu."
  54,25,"Niye butswa yenyene okhurula mwifwe wamakanyiliso keshela? Halali uno nomubeyi omukhongo, omufuru.”"
  54,26,"Nibamanye mutsuli niwina omubeeyi omukhongo, omufuru."
  54,27,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhubarumila ingamia ikhasi khulwa okhubatema, mana bahenge butswa ne wifwile."
  54,28,"Ne baboolele mbu amatsi kalakabwa hakari wabu (nende ingamia) mana inyanga yabu yokhunywa amatsi ne iyaga yindi ye ingamia."
  54,29,"Mana nibalaanga omundu wabu, niyetsa mana nayisinza."
  54,30,"Kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje?"
  54,31,"Toto efwe khwabarumila olwang’a lulala lwonyene, nibaba shinga ebitiisi biokhumbashila olukaka."
  54,32,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu khubwitsulisio, ne koo aliwo witsulila?"
  54,33,"Abandu ba Luti bayingasia Abekanyilisi."
  54,34,"Toto efwe khwabarumila eshifulumutu shiamachina, halali abaloondi ba Luti, khwabahabina mumabwibwi."
  54,35,"Tsimbabaasi okhurula khwifwe. Endio nilwa khurunganga ulia ukhupanga orio muno."
  54,36,"Ne toto ye yabekanyilisilia eshinyasio shiefu, halali bo bali netsinganakani khumekanyilisio ako."
  54,37,"Ne toto benya mbu abahelesie abacheni be, mana nikhubawofusia tsimoni tsiabu, nikhubaboolela mbu: “Pile eshinyasio shianje nende amekanyilisio.”"
  54,38,"Ne toto shiabeeshela eshinyasio shitsililila mumabwibi."
  54,39,"Kho mana pile eshinyasio shianje nende amekanyilisio."
  54,40,"Ne toto khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu khubwitsulisio, ne koo aliwo witsulila?"
  54,41,"Ne toto Abekanyilisi betsela Abandu ba Firauni."
  54,42,"Bakhaya ebimanyisio biefu bioosi pe, mana nikhubatila omutilo kwa Wamaani, Wobunyali po."
  54,43,"Ne Abakhayi benyu bali nende amaani okhushila abo baranjilila, nohomba kahandikwa mubitabu mbu enywe mubule okhufunaanibwa tawe?"
  54,44,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “Efwe khuli abaanji khulishila butswa.”"
  54,45,"Abanji abo balashilwa ne balakalukha inyuma tsimbilo."
  54,46,"Halali inyanga yeyindukho niyabalakwa. Ne indukho ni isiro muno mana khandi indulu pa."
  54,47,"Toto Abetsimbi bali mubukori nende mubulalu."
  54,48,"Inyanga yabalikhwesurulwa mafumama khubweni bwabu nibasukunwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu: “Pile omutilo kwomulilo kwa Saqar.”"
  54,49,"Toto efwe buli eshindu khwashiloonga khushichelo shiabura inyuma."
  54,50,"Ne likhuwa liefu nililala butswa, shinga okhulimba nende okhulimbula tsimoni."
  54,51,"Ne toto khwasishia abashienywe, kho alikho mwinywe witsulilanga?"
  54,52,"Ne koosi kabakhola kali mubitabu."
  54,53,"Ne liosiliosi lititi nende likhonga liahandikwa."
  54,54,"Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda chomwikulu nende emialo."
  54,55,"Mushikhalo shiatoto, ewa Omwami, Omunyali muno."
